      "title": "What is a Preset? / 什么是 Preset？",
      "text": "A Preset node wraps a backend workflow and exposes only the controls users need: prompt, media slots, model readiness, configs, and Run. / Preset 节点封装后端工作流，只暴露用户需要的提示词、媒体槽、模型状态、配置和运行入口。",
